Package: transformUI
Title: Graphical user interface for transformation functions for flow cytometry data
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Stephan", "Benke", email = "s.benke@cytometry.uzh.ch",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a graphical user interface for some of the transformation functions in flowCore. 
  Automated transformation paramter estimation is supported for logicle (via estimateLogicle in flowCore) 
  and asinh (via estParamFlowVS in flowVS) transformations.
Depends: 
  R (>= 3.6.0),
  flowCore (>= 2.0.1)
Imports:
  flowVS,
  miniUI,
  shiny,
  ggplot2,
  purrr,
  stringr,
  tibble
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
